Guidances:
  Lamda's or serverless AWS support limited number of languages
  Asynchronous reponse - where a waiting period is high - then Lamda are not good thing
  Hybrid or Multi cloud environment helps Dockers or containers
  
  How stateful appliactions is? As Lamda are stateless
  
  Common UseCases?
    1) Webapplication - static website, complex website - Lamda
    2) Autonomous IT - Lamda
    3) Backends  - lamda
    4) Data processing - Lamda
    5) Chatbots - Lamda
    6) Amazon Alexa - Lamda









